# Final outputs (reviews.csv/json, tagged.csv/json, summary_tables.json,
# six_question_answers.json, pipeline_summary.json) ARE committed on purpose:
# the deployed Streamlit dashboard only reads saved data under data/, it
# never scrapes or calls an LLM itself, so the repo needs real data checked in
# to be inspectable out of the box. Only the pre-recency-filter raw dump and
# the on-disk LLM response cache are excluded, since neither is needed to run
# the dashboard and both are regenerated by run_pipeline.py.
data/reviews_raw.csv
data/reviews_raw.json
data/llm_cache/
data/stress_test_llm_cache/
